	<div class="item_desc_text justify">
	<p>Villa ivn pirin golf is located in the territory of 5-star complex pirin golf &amp; country club in all 10 km from the international ski resort Bansko.</p>

	<p>Villa is located on its own fenced evergreen trees land 900 m2 with lawn, Pine trees and 2 parking places under the canopy.</p>

	<p>Total area Villas 195 m2, consists of 3 bedrooms, 2 bathroom, kitchen, living room and dining area, Terrace with the area barbecue, as well as technical room, guest toilet and pantry. All rooms furnishings solid wood, walls and ceilings finished with wooden panels. Of the panoramic window opens great Mountain view, Forest and golf course.</p>

	<p>Living room is equipped with fireplace, big TV with the flat screens and satellite channels, system home theatre and dvd player. Kitchen is equipped with a dishwasher, oven, electric stove, microwave oven, toaster, kettle and a large fridge. Bathrooms are equipped with bath accessories, bathrobes, towels, slippers.</p>

	<p>In the territory of the complex Pirin Golf &amp; Country Club offers: professional golf course international level, Spa, gym, ski school, golf club, driving golf course and golf school, as well as restaurants, shops, supermarket, playground, indoor and outdoor pools, billiard room. Also works rental ski, bike and equipment golf course. equip storage ski, golf game in the table tennis.</p>

	<p>Distance to the airport Sofia is 160 km. Ski lift Bansko 12 km.</p>
</div>

